<Content_wSideColumn ID="x36032" Name="Forwarding" Layout="byuidefault.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Forward BYU-Idaho email to another email address</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Forward BYU-Idaho email to another email address</Abstract><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="SideColumn" label="L/R Column" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><MoveLeft type="boolean" label="Toggle column right or left (right is default)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</MoveLeft><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="ImageComponent" label="Image Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="LeftColumnImageComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="TextComponent" label="Text Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="ColumnTextComponent"/><fbookTop type="boolean" label="Put facebook at top of page" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</fbookTop><fbookStatus type="string" label="Facebook ID#" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookStatus><fbookToken type="string" label="Access_Token" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookToken><fbookDisplayed type="string" label="Number of facebook messages to display" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">1</fbookDisplayed></xPower><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<div>
<p align="center"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">(Instructions for Internet Explorer web browsers only) </span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Log into your email account through my.byui.edu and do the following: </span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">1. Click </span><strong style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Rules</strong><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;"> on the lower left corner of the window. If Rules is not showing, click on the small blue arrow above the icons&nbsp;in the lower left corner&nbsp;to expand the view to display Rules.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">2. Click </span><strong style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">New.</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">3. Click </span><strong style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Forward it to</strong><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;"> and then enter the email address you want it sent to.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">4. If you would like, uncheck </span><strong style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Keep a copy in my Inbox</strong><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;"> (although you would still need to empty out your deleted items folder occasionally so you would not exceed your storage limit).</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">5.Click </span><strong style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Save and Close</strong><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Other client instructions coming soon!</span></p>
